OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fbut with an isolated shower possible.
OL,7,FLate sunny spells in the evening,
OL,8,Fleading to clear spells overnight.
OL,9,FBreezy near the coast at first before
OL,10,Feasing later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA largely dry day with
OL,13,Fbright and sunny spells in the
OL,14,Fmorning. Turning cloudier through the
OL,15,Fafternoon with light rain spreading
OL,16,Feastwards in the evening. Light winds.
